quizzes.textContent:
[h1]Relational Operators [/h1]

You can use relational operators to compare variables in the [b]if[/b] statement.
[b]For example:[/b] [code format="cpp" codeId="194"]int a = 55;
int b = 33;
if (a > b) {
  cout << "a is greater than b";
}

// Outputs "a is greater than b"[/code]
